{"tid":599071,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"深水埗賊偷手機殼 遭5壯男綁腳制服","createTime":"2018-03-20T05:50:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-20T08:02:31.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"7e44421b016f798662670414e9cd84f8fe895cbb","tid":599071,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T05:50:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180320/20337752\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180320%2F20337752&d=Z%2Bo1ZBmCoAcqYYG%2BOstpWnIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=43c4c666\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180320%2F20337752&h=af423247\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180320/20337752</a><br />\n<br />\n深水埗賊偷手機殼<br />\n遭5壯男綁腳制服<br />\n<br />\n港聞   <br />\n         <br />\n【本報訊】深水埗發生偷竊案。一名32歲男子前日下午4時許進入深水埗福華街「深水埗電子特賣場」佯裝購物，然而被店員揭發偷了一個手機殼，上前喝止，疑犯見事敗一度欲逃走，惟被兩名店員及3名熱心途人合力制服，等候警員到場處理。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n根據巿民提供長約4分鐘的現場片段，可見該名小偷被制服後，仍在福華街地上不斷掙扎反抗。據目擊的盧先生表示，當日下午約4時50分，他途經現場附近買完外賣，見到深水埗電子特賣場職員和兩名熱心男制服該名小偷後，一度發生混戰，就連小偷上身的牛仔恤及波鞋亦飛脫，一度赤裸上身，一名穿着便服的中年店員見狀，就地取材取來附近竹棚的繩索，紮住疑犯的左腳並吊起，疑犯不斷大喊：「(隻腳)斷啦！」職員隨即勸喻疑犯：「你坐低我放你！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n然而店員為疑犯鬆綁後，此時，剛好警車正響號駛至，疑犯聽到響號再度情緒激動，不斷企圖突破重圍逃跑。另一名途經現場的余先生亦目擊情況，見到一名大男人被數名熱心途人合力壓在地上，最後由到場的警員接手，並將疑犯拉到後巷鎖上手銬帶走。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警方回應稱，一名32歲男子在福華街一間店舖偷去一個價值200元的手機殼，涉嫌店舖盜竊被捕，混亂中一名68歲姓陳男職員在制服賊人時手部受輕傷，經救護員到場敷治後拒絕送院。"},{"pid":"7f699943250c0dc8662492e86136c5c0682e35bd","tid":599071,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T05:57:24.000Z","msg":"Diu, 我唔想撲野呀.jpg"},{"pid":"6e957ff2323aa030e2ccfc1f3298cf1fce9b759e","tid":599071,"uid":156005,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T06:23:00.000Z","msg":"呢間野d手機殼好撚平架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n價值200元的手機殼？連埋尿袋果d？"},{"pid":"07b7755d919a40ed988639bac55e25f5dd6a99c7","tid":599071,"uid":51532,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T07:01:31.000Z","msg":"呢間野咁開放式唔偷都對唔住自己"},{"pid":"07f4c035b2b1d50f230bc4aeb91fc937efa13114","tid":599071,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T07:05:30.000Z","msg":"咁撚正義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f39c32178a87dfb021ac9dae80d0792a9d88c96","tid":599071,"uid":102096,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T07:08:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"312563fa527fee1525e4ebbf7a45bc2ecd00737c","tid":599071,"uid":157171,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"3f39c32178a87dfb021ac9dae80d0792a9d88c96","tid":599071,"uid":102096,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T07:08:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T07:38:49.000Z","msg":"你咪仲廢, 人地起碼去捉小偷。你呢? 係到呀支呀左, ON99 咁"},{"pid":"f0258e44f6edbc55d2ea28f46adff014b5d66305","tid":599071,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"3f39c32178a87dfb021ac9dae80d0792a9d88c96","tid":599071,"uid":102096,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T07:08:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T07:46:53.000Z","msg":"蝻亞人都算半個鬼佬，要俾少少面，盡地主之誼"},{"pid":"63e05a161cb766289baad4ec9c5ba68e0dddf00e","tid":599071,"uid":129221,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T07:48:52.000Z","msg":"又系蝗搞事啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cea32cc2c89b716af727ab11ff015d1c191af30","tid":599071,"uid":123296,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"63e05a161cb766289baad4ec9c5ba68e0dddf00e","tid":599071,"uid":129221,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T07:48:52.000Z","msg":"又系蝗搞事啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"